
<% layout("layouts/boilerplate.ejs") %>


<style>
  body {
    font-family: sans-serif;
  }

  header {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .search-bar {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .accordion-button::after {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767.98px) {
    header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .search-bar {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .search-bar input {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
<header class="container py-3">
  <h1>Sproutly Help Center</h1>
</header>

<main class="container py-5">
  <section class="accordion" id="accordion">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1">
          How do I place an order?
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          <p>Placing an order on Sproutly is easy! Simply browse our selection of fresh produce, add items to your cart, and proceed to checkout. You can choose your delivery date and time during checkout.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
          Can I customize my order after it's placed?
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          <p>Unfortunately, you cannot directly modify your order once it's confirmed. However, you can contact our customer support team as soon as possible after placing your order to see if changes are still feasible. We'll do our best to accommodate your request.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
          What are the minimum order requirements?
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          <p>Sproutly has a minimum order value of Rs. 199 to ensure efficient delivery operations. You can see the current minimum order value displayed in your cart before checkout.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
          Do you offer subscriptions for regular deliveries?
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          <p>Currently, Sproutly doesn't offer subscription services. However, we encourage you to check out our "Pre-Order" section for frequently purchased items you can schedule for recurring deliveries.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq5">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
          What are your delivery fees?
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq5" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          <p>Currently, Sproutly's delivery fees depend on your delivery address. This allows us to offer competitive pricing based on location and delivery distance. But we offer free delivery for orders above Rs. 1000.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq6">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
          How do I change my delivery address?
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div id="collapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq6" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          <p>Sproutly allows you to choose between your saved delivery addresses and a new address during checkout. Here's how:

            Scenario 1: Using a Saved Delivery Address
            
            During checkout, you'll see a section labeled "Delivery Address."
            A dropdown menu or list will display your saved delivery addresses.
            Simply select the address you want to use for this order from the list.

            Scenario 2: Delivering to a New Address
            
            If you want to deliver to an address different from your saved ones, fill out the form for the New Address.
            A complete address form will appear, allowing you to enter details like:
            First & Last Name
            Street Address
            City
            State/Province
            Zip Code
            Phone Number
            Once you've filled out the new address form, proceed with the checkout process.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h3 class="accordion-header" id="faq7">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse7">
          How do I contact customer support?
        </button>
      </h3>
      <div id="collapse7" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq7" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          <p>Visit our dedicated Contact Us page on our website <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>. This page provides a contact form where you can submit your inquiry and leave your email address for a response.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="container py-3 text-center">
  <p>Still have questions? <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></p>
</footer>









